PrecisOrder directing that a proclamation do issue giving notice that the Protocol amending the Convention between the Government of Canada and the Government of ITALY for the avoidance of double taxation with respect to taxes on income and for the prevention of fiscal evasion came into force, pursuant to Article 2 of the Protocol, on February 22, 1994.
